nodes.name: Format Fields to something Nice again

parameters.pythonCode:
hour = 0
min = 5
sec = 0

for item in _input.all():
  time = item.json['Total Time'].split(":") 
  hour+=int(time[0])
  min+=int(time[1])
  sec+=int(time[2])

# Format Sec to Mintue
if sec > 59:
  sec -= 60
  min += 1
# Add Leading 0
if sec < 10:
  sec = f"0{str(sec)}"
# Format Min to Hour
if min > 59:
  min -= 60
  hour += 1
# Add Leading 0
if min < 10:
  min = f"0{str(min)}"
# Add Leading 0
if hour < 10:
  hour = f"0{str(hour)}"
return {'totalTime':f'{hour}:{min}:{sec}'}
